{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"eval 函數","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Functions_effb9b1bcc102a5f6df7f1785ce89033","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"onlyinclude\" id=\"sect1\">\n<h4 id=\"eval_函數\" name=\"eval_函數\">eval 函數</h4>\n<p><code>eval</code> 函數無須參考實際的物件，就可以對 JavaScript 代碼的字串直接求值。eval 語法如下︰</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">eval(expr)\n</pre>\n<p>此處 <code>expr</code> 就是要被求值的字串。</p>\n<p>如果字串表示成表達式，<code>eval</code> 就會對表達式求值。如果參數（<code>expr</code>）表示成一個以上的 JavaScript 語句，eval 就會對語句求值。<code>eval</code> 代碼的作用域等同於呼叫端代碼的作用域。不要用 <code>eval</code> 來對算術表達式求值，JavaScript 會自動的對算術表達式來求值。</p>\n</div>\n<p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/預先定義的函數\">« 前頁</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/預先定義的函數/isFinite_函數\">次頁  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"eval 函數無須參考實際的物件，就可以對 JavaScript 代碼的字串直接求值。eval 語法如下︰","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"locale":"en-US","title":"Functions","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/functions_effb9b1bcc102a5f6df7f1785ce89033","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/functions_effb9b1bcc102a5f6df7f1785ce89033/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide","title":"陣列的運用"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Functions_effb9b1bcc102a5f6df7f1785ce89033","title":"eval 函數"}],"pageTitle":"eval 函數 | MDN","noIndexing":true}}